data.description: Welcome home to your move-in ready updated ranch with 3 BR, 1 FB in sought-after Island Heights.  Located in a prime location, 1 block to the bay beach & close to riverfront park, library, post office & promenade.  Enter into the spacious LR opening to the DR and kitchen. Enjoy the river views from your deck, LR, DR, kitchen & your BR.  Many upgrades-kitchen with granite counters, SS appliances & center island, new 50 year Timberline roof, new electric, windows, doors, heating & cooling, tankless WH, refinished wood floors, light fixtures, fans, vents, freshly painted in & out & new landscape.  Plenty of room to relax or entertain on the newly painted 2-tier deck with new electric & gas grill.  Unfinished basement has laundry room, framed, ready to go. Offers are due on Wednesday, April 24 at 5:00 PM.
